## Internal docs (local only — public repo, keep sensitive planning private)
## Option K layout: docs/specs/, docs/decisions/, docs/research/ are PUBLIC
## (tracked). docs/plans/ defaults to local until each plan is reviewed for
## cross-repo/commercial leakage; explicitly tracked plans can live in
## docs/plans/active|completed|archived/ after review — use `git add -f`.
## Anything referencing private-repo paths, commercial roadmap, pricing or
## partner info lives in docs/superpowers/ (never pushed).
